tified crew installs to Title 24 standards, completes city inspections, and leaves your  home spotless.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="f-section-large-4"><div class="f-margin-bottom-132"><div class="f-title-wrapper-center-2"><div class="f-margin-bottom-130"><div class="f-heading-detail-small-3"><strong>Why Deluxe Windows</strong></div></div><div class="f-margin-bottom-131"><div class="f-h3-heading w-embed">Your Trusted San Francisco Window Experts</div></div></div></div><div class="container-default"><div class="w-layout-grid f-grid-two-column"><div class="f-feature-card-outlined"><div class="f-margin-bottom-133"><div class="f-h5-heading-2 w-embed">30+ Years Serving San Francisco</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8cfc69cacbe37d86ee97e_Serving.png" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8cfc69cacbe37d86ee97e_Serving-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8cfc69cacbe37d86ee97e_Serving.png 510w" alt="" class="image-39"/></div><div class="w-embed">We've installed thousands of windows across the Bay Area, including hundreds of homes in San Francisco and San Francisco County. We know local building codes, permit requirements, and what works best for your neighborhood's architecture.</div></div><div class="f-feature-card-outlined"><div class="f-margin-bottom-133"><div class="f-h5-heading-2 w-embed">100% Employee Owned</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d289211bd2f16110f2b0_100%25%20employee.png" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d289211bd2f16110f2b0_100%25%20employee-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d289211bd2f16110f2b0_100%25%20employee.png 510w" alt="" class="image-39"/></div><div class="w-embed">Every person on your project has a personal stake in doing excellent work. No subcontractors, no turnover — the same dedicated team from estimate through installation and warranty service.</div></div><div class="f-feature-card-outlined"><div class="f-margin-bottom-133"><div class="f-h5-heading-2 w-embed">Full Permit Management</div></div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39105ebed7c883bd0d7_Permit.png" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39105ebed7c883bd0d7_Permit-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39105ebed7c883bd0d7_Permit.png 510w" alt="" class="image-39"/><div class="w-embed">We handle all San Francisco city permits, filings, and inspections from start to finish. You don't have to navigate city hall — we've done it hundreds of times and know exactly what's required.</div></div><div class="f-feature-card-outlined"><div class="f-margin-bottom-133"><div class="f-h5-heading-2 w-embed">Flexible Financing</div></div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39e3f48002cc0bdf747_financing.png" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39e3f48002cc0bdf747_financing-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69d8d39e3f48002cc0bdf747_financing.png 510w" alt="" class="image-39"/><div class="w-embed">Spread the cost of your San Francisco window project with our flexible financing plans. Low monthly payments, competitive rates — ask about current financing offers when you request your free estimate.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="f-section-large-3"><div class="f-container-regular-3"><div class="f-margin-bottom-64"><div class="w-layout-grid f-header-grid-asymmetrical"><div id="w-node-_62415541-8aa0-a03d-fd67-04e3ce71fbe3-ce71fbdf" class="f-max-width-large"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6841ddf8ace3d9d9facb14fd/69986ae97432d22237832ac2_guarantee-icon.svg" loading="lazy" width="100" alt=""/><h3 class="f-h3-heading-2">Our Guarantee</h3></div></div></div><div class="w-layout-grid f-grid-three-column-2"><div class="f-feature-card-filled"><div class="f-margin-bottom-129"><h5 class="f-h5-heading">Vinyl windows<br/>‍</h5></div><p class="f-paragraph-large-2"><strong><br/>Full lifetime</strong> transferable warranty on parts and labor</p></div><div class="f-feature-card-filled"><div class="f-margin-bottom-129"><h5 class="f-h5-heading">Aluminum Wood clad, fiberglass, fiberglass clad</h5></div><p class="f-paragraph-large-2"><br/>Offer <strong>20 year</strong> on glass.</p></div><div class="f-feature-card-filled"><div class="f-margin-bottom-129"><h5 class="f-h5-heading">All Other Parts<br/>‍</h5></div><p class="f-paragraph-large-2"><strong><br/>10 Years</strong> Warranty</p></div></div><p class="f-paragraph-large-2 dsaf">Manufacturer&#x27;s warranty on glass and frame - lifetime**</p></div></div><section><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-default w-container"><div class="w-embed w-script"><!-- Elfsight All-in-One Reviews | Untitled All-in-One Reviews 2 -->
